ikely-be-in-the-dark-phoenix |title=Two Major X-Men Characters Who Will Likely Be in the Dark Phoenix |last=Wakeman |first=Gregory |work=Cinema Blend |date=May 20, 2017 |access-date=April 27, 2017 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6rWVkf3js?url=http://www.cinemablend.com/news/1660810/two-major-x-men-characters-who-will-likely-be-in-the-dark-phoenix |archive-date=June 27, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ParkerCosmic\">{{cite news |url=https://screenrant.com/x-men-dark-phoenix-cosmic/ |title=X-Men: Dark Phoenix Going Cosmic 'Certainly a Possibility' |last=Keyes |first=Rob |work=Screen Rant |date=May 23, 2017 |access-date=June 27, 2017 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6rWVpNzlR?url=http://screenrant.com/x-men-dark-phoenix-cosmic/ |archive-date=June 27, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Shi'ar\">{{cite news |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/x-men/news/a830307/x-men-dark-phoenix-shiar-aliens/ |title=X-Men: Dark Phoenix could bring us some classic Marvel aliens, the Shi'ar |last=Armitage |first=Hugh |work=[[Digital Spy]] |date=June 8, 2017 |access-date=June 27, 2017 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6rWVsvJTN?url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/x-men/news/a830307/x-men-dark-phoenix-shiar-aliens/ |archive-date=June 27, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"JolieChastain\">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbr.com/x-men-dark-phoenix-casting-rumors-angelina-jolie-jessica-chastain/ |title=X-Men: Dark Phoenix Casting Rumors Include Jolie, Chastain |last=Sobon |first=Nicole |work=[[Comic Book Resources]] |date=June 9, 2017 |access-date=June 27, 2017 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6rWVzXLK7?url=http://www.cbr.com/x-men-dark-phoenix-casting-rumors-angelina-jolie-jessica-chastain/ |archive-date=June 27, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"FormalizedPlans\">{{cite news |url=https://deadline.com/2017/06/x-men-dark-phoenix-jennifer-lawrence-michael-fassbender-james-mcavoy-simon-kinberg-1202113290/ |title=Fox Forma